#: ../../source/module/baesx.rst:10 492435aa70034bcd885da9883902e0bf
msgid ""
"BaseX is an M5Stack stackable module with 4 DC motor channels and 2 servo"
" channels. It communicates with the host via I2C address ``0x22``. The "
"onboard controller handles motor PWM output, motor encoder count, "
"position/speed mode configuration, and servo output."
msgstr "BaseX 是 M5Stack 可堆叠模块，提供 4 路直流电机通道和 2 路舵机通道。它通过 I2C 地址 ``0x22`` 与主机通信。板载控制器负责电机 PWM 输出、电机编码器计数、位置/速度模式配置以及舵机输出。"

